PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Transport of EDWARD C. BRUCE of Long Harbour, Newfoundland and Labrador, as a member of the Atlantic Pilotage Authority, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Donna Pardy, whose term has expired.
